commits.content:
# Firebase Configuration
# Replace with your actual Firebase project values

FIREBASE_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your-project-id.firebaseapp.com
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your-project-id.appspot.com
FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your-sender-id
FIREBASE_APP_ID=your-app-id
FIREBASE_DATABASE_URL=https://your-project-id-default-rtdb.firebaseio.com/

# Netlify Configuration (automatically set by Netlify)
# These are used for form submissions and site functionality
NETLIFY_SITE_ID=your-netlify-site-id
NETLIFY_SITE_URL=https://your-site-name.netlify.app

# Optional: Email notification settings
ADMIN_EMAIL=hello@nexustech.dev
NOTIFICATION_EMAIL=notifications@nexustech.dev
